      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/optimization/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.52,
      "size": 40320,
      "text": "生活中我们经常面临优化问题：如何用最少的成本获得最大的收益？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "optimization",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/optimization/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.82,
      "size": 29088,
      "text": "如何规划最短的路线？如何分配有限的资源？"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "optimization",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-4",
      "filename": "intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/optimization/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.71,
      "size": 27360,
      "text": "数学优化为这些问题提供了系统的解决方法。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "optimization",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-1",
      "filename": "concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/optimization/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.12,
      "size": 33840,
      "text": "优化问题的目标是找到使某个函数取得最大或最小值的点。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "optimization",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-2",
      "filename": "concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/optimization/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.84,
      "size": 29376,
      "text": "这个函数叫做目标函数，要找的点叫做最优解。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "optimization",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-3",
      "filename": "concept-concept-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/optimization/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.43,
      "size": 38880,
      "text": "如果没有限制条件，叫做无约束优化；有限制条件，叫做约束优化。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "optimization",
      "section_id": "concept",
      "line_id": "concept-4",
      "filename": "concept-concept-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/optimization/xiaoxiao/concept-concept-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.07,
      "size": 17136,
      "text": "让我们从最简单的情况开始。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "optimization",
      "section_id": "unconstrained",
      "line_id": "uncon-1",
      "filename": "unconstrained-uncon-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/optimization/xiaoxiao/unconstrained-uncon-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.47,
      "size": 23472,
      "text": "对于光滑函数，极值点处的梯度为零。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "optimization",
      "section_id": "unconstrained",
      "line_id": "uncon-2",
      "filename": "unconstrained-uncon-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/optimization/xiaoxiao/unconstrained-uncon-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.7,
      "size": 27216,
      "text": "这给了我们寻找极值的方向：沿着梯度下降。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "optimization",
      "section_id": "unconstrained",
      "line_id": "uncon-3",
      "filename": "unconstrained-uncon-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/optimization/xiaoxiao/unconstrained-uncon-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.56,
      "size": 24912,
      "text": "梯度下降法就是不断沿着负梯度方向移动。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "optimization",
      "section_id": "unconstrained",
      "line_id": "uncon-4",
      "filename": "unconstrained-uncon-4.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/optimization/xiaoxiao/unconstrained-uncon-4.mp3",
      "duration": 1.41,
      "size": 22608,
      "text": "观察点如何逐步接近函数的最小值。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "optimization",
      "section_id": "constrained",
      "line_id": "con-1",
      "filename": "constrained-con-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/optimization/xiaoxiao/constrained-con-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.43,
      "size": 22896,
      "text": "现实中的优化问题通常有约束条件。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "optimization",
